 <body ><br><h1 class="pHead1" >
assert_handshake
</h1>    
<a name="wp3731043"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that specified request and acknowledge signals follow a specified handshake protocol.  </p>    <div align="left" class="tbl">
