  <p class="pBody" >
</p>    
<a name="wp3751985"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that multiple <code class="cCodeBody">hold</code> requests are not made while waiting for a <code class="cCodeBody">holda</code> acknowledge and that every <code class="cCodeBody">holda</code> acknowledge is in response to a unique <code class="cCodeBody">hold</code> request.  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkers50.gif" height="89" width="428" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
  <p class="pBody" >  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkers68.gif" height="95" width="432" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
  <p class="pBody" >
</p>    
<a name="wp3752381"> </a><p class="pBody" >
After a violation, checking is turned off until <code class="cCodeBody">holda</code> acknowledge is sampled deasserted.  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkers47.gif" height="91" width="432" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
  <p class="pBody" >
</p>    
