<a name="wp3756944"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that multiple <code class="cCodeBody">hold</code> requests are not made while waiting for a <code class="cCodeBody">holda</code> acknowledge and that every <code class="cCodeBody">holda</code> acknowledge is in response to a unique <code class="cCodeBody">hold</code> request. Ensures <code class="cCodeBody">hold</code> request remains asserted until its <code class="cCodeBody">holda</code> acknowledge and then deasserts in the next cycle.  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkers73.gif" height="89" width="432" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
